<section class="raffle-faq">
  <h2 class="raffle-faq__title">Questions</h2>

  <details class="raffle-faq__item">
    <summary class="raffle-faq__q">Is there an age limit for the raffle?</summary>
    <p class="raffle-faq__a">
      As long as you are above the age of 13, anyone is eligible for the raffle! However, only people who
      are 18 or below are eligible for the main Stardance program and so you can only refer people &lt;=18.
    </p>
  </details>

  <details class="raffle-faq__item">
    <summary class="raffle-faq__q">How does the raffle work?</summary>
    <p class="raffle-faq__a">
      Every week for 16 weeks we give away one AMD Radeon RX 9060 XT. You earn tickets for that week by
      referring participants 13-18 who join Stardance and verify themselves.
    </p>
  </details>

  <details class="raffle-faq__item">
    <summary class="raffle-faq__q">How do I earn tickets?</summary>
    <p class="raffle-faq__a">
      Share your referral link. Every participant who joins through it and verifies their ID earns you
      <strong class="raffle-pop">+20 tickets</strong> toward that week's draw.
    </p>
  </details>

  <details class="raffle-faq__item">
    <summary class="raffle-faq__q">What are my odds of winning?</summary>
    <p class="raffle-faq__a">
      Each week one GPU is drawn. Your odds are your tickets divided by every ticket in that week's pool,
      so the more verified participants you bring, the better your chances.
    </p>
  </details>

  <details class="raffle-faq__item">
    <summary class="raffle-faq__q">Do tickets carry over between weeks?</summary>
    <p class="raffle-faq__a">
      No, each week starts fresh. Tickets count toward the week they were earned in, so there's a new
      chance to win every single week.
    </p>
  </details>

  <details class="raffle-faq__item">
    <summary class="raffle-faq__q">Is it free to enter?</summary>
    <p class="raffle-faq__a">
      Yes. It's free, with no purchase necessary, just sign in with GitHub and share your link.
    </p>
  </details>
</section>
